|>    Hmmm.  I haven't seen the algorithms to RC2 or RC4 published here, though
|> there's been a fair amount of talk about them, they're implemented in
|> software, and PKP's lawyers are *much* less intimidating that the US Gov't's
|> Justice Dept., when trying to make an example of someone.
